    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {className: a3; text-indent: 48px;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a5 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Иқтисодий ишлар бўйича <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган иқтисодий суди номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">га</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Манзил: </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ариза берувчининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ариза берувчи юридик шахс номи ёки якка тартибдаги тадбиркор (ЯТТ)нинг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">томонидан</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Мол-мулкни хатлаш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Иқтисодий </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">ишлар</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ариза берувчининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> судининг иш юритувида даъвогар </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Иш бўйича даъвогар ташкилотнинг ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли ва номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">нинг жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Иш бўйича жавобгар ташкилотнинг ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли ва номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">га нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Даъво ариза мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> ҳақидаги иқтисодий иш мавжуд.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Ушбу иқтисодий иш кўриб чиқилгунга қадар, даъвони таъминлаш чораларини кўрмаслик суд </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">ижросини қийинлаштириб, уни бажариб бўлмайдиган қилиб қўйиши эҳтимоли борлиги сабабли, жавобгарга тегишли бўлган мол-мулкларни хатлаш </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">мақсадга мувофиқ бўлади.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Юқоридагилардан келиб чиқиб, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Иқтисодий процессуал кодексининг 94-96-моддаларига асосланиб,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">СЎРАЙМАН:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Мазкур иқтисодий иш бўйича мол-мулкни хатлаш ҳақидаги аризамни қаноатлантиришингизни;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Жавобгарга тегишли бўлган барча мол-мулкларни иш бўйича якуний хулосага келингунига қадар хатлашингизни.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Ариза берувчи юридик шахс раҳбарининг ёки якка тартибдаги тадбиркор (ЯТТ)нинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.14404432133px;\">\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
